   1:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp **** /**
   2:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp ****  * dac_breathing_led.cpp â€” Breathing LEDs on DAC1, DAC2, and ADC0 (chained)
   3:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp ****  * Daisy Seed
   4:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp ****  *
   5:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp ****  * Three LEDs chained as a rolling wave. Each LED does a rise â†’ hold â†’
   6:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp ****  * fall breath; each new LED starts the moment the previous one reaches
   7:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp ****  * 100%.
   8:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp ****  *
   9:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp ****  *   phase   0    R    2R    3R   3R+H   4R+H=1
  10:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp ****  *   LED1    0 â†’ 100 â†’ 100 â†’ 0
  11:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp ****  *   LED2         0 â†’ 100 â†’ 100 â†’ 0
  12:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp ****  *   LED3              0 â†’ 100 â†’ 100 â†’ 0
  13:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp ****  *
  14:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp ****  * Outputs:
  15:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp ****  *   LED1 â†’ DAC OUT 1 (pin 30, analog 0â€“3.3V)
  16:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp ****  *   LED2 â†’ DAC OUT 2 (pin 31, analog 0â€“3.3V)
ARM GAS  /var/folders/1t/pyvz513s4fs9l00kxmc709xh0000gp/T//cchp3PZh.s 			page 9


  17:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp ****  *   LED3 â†’ A0 / ADC0 (pin 22) â€” software PWM, GPIO toggled at ~2 kHz
  18:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp ****  *
  19:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp ****  * Wiring (each LED): anode â†’ output pin â†’ ~330R â†’ cathode â†’ GND.
  20:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp ****  */
  21:tools/dac_breathing_led.cpp **** 
